{
  "stem": "2539.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So because she found out I had nowhere to stay in Kiev-- I told her on the truck that I've got nothing to-- nothing-- nowhere to stay.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, stay with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the first night in Kiev, I stayed with her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the boy died the second night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I found myself-- I found myself in a funeral procession through Kiev, after arrival in Kiev-- very soon after.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, I want to tell you another incident happened in Kiev, very briefly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I met-- I don't whom I met.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how I met.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was invited to some people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were having a party.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't forget there was curfew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So when it got dark, you couldn't walk out on the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I probably didn't realize that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, we were sitting and talking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we all stayed there overnight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All of us stayed in the one big room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everybody who attended the party stayed there-- women and men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There would have been-- I don't know-- about 12 of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I slept on the couch, on the settee, in the middle of the room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were sleeping on the-- on the beds, and on the floor-- on the floor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Towards the morning, I hear-- I was very uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I hear someone saying-- oh, maybe it was when we-- when the lights were turned off.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I heard a man saying-- saying the following-- she will be dead tomorrow morning, that [NON-ENGLISH], that-- that Jewess.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She'll be dead tomorrow morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now when I heard that, of course I couldn't sleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, I couldn't fall asleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I had to have a plan.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How am I going to escape this?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't go now, it's dark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, somebody on the street would shoot me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
